OL,3,CMan jailed for multiple rapes dating
OL,4,Cback more than two decades
OL,6,FA man from Neath has been jailed for
OL,7,F24 years for multiple rapes and sexual
OL,8,Fassaults in Cardiff that date back
OL,9,Fmore than 20 years.
OL,11,FAn investigation began in 2019, when a
OL,12,Fvictim bravely came forward to report
OL,13,Fto that they had been raped by John
OL,14,FCharles Webb.
OL,16,FWebb, now aged 70, was arrested at his
OL,17,Fhome address in Neath.
OL,19,FAs a result of enquiries, two other
OL,20,Fvictims were also identified and they
OL,21,Fprovided statements.
