OL,6,FAll three victims, two male and one
OL,7,Ffemale, were under the age of 18 at
OL,8,Fthe time of the sexual assaults which
OL,9,Fhappened in the 1990s while Webb was
OL,10,Fliving in Cardiff.
OL,12,FWebb was charged and faced trial at in
OL,13,FDecember 2023.
OL,15,FHe was found guilty of all 21 sexual
OL,16,Foffences including three counts of
OL,17,Frape, five indecent assaults, and
OL,18,Fseven counts of indecent assault on a
OL,19,Fmale.
