OL,6,FWebb was sentenced at the same court
OL,7,Fon Friday, 8 March to 24 years in
OL,8,Fprison.
OL,10,FOfficer in the case, Detective
OL,11,FConstable Jenna Hargraves, said:
OL,12,F"Webb's actions have taken a massive
OL,13,Femotional toll on all three victims.
OL,15,F"For one of them, their life headed
OL,16,Ftowards criminality because they
OL,17,Fstruggled to cope with what had
OL,18,Fhappened. Another victim described
OL,19,FWebb as a violent man.
