OL,6,F"But thanks to their bravery and a
OL,7,Fthorough investigation, he has been
OL,8,Fbrought to justice. South Wales Police
OL,9,Ftakes all reports of sexual violence
OL,10,Fextremely seriously and it is never
OL,11,Ftoo late to report a crime."
OL,13,FHe added: "Help and support is
OL,14,Favailable for all victims of sexual
OL,15,Fviolence, and we would encourage any
OL,16,Fvictims; no matter how long ago the
OL,17,Foffence happened, to please come
OL,18,Fforward.
